                            <comment id="318293" author="adilger" created="Mon, 15 Nov 2021 21:24:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;NB: this was originally &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15232&quot; title=&quot;sanity-lnet : @@@@@@ FAIL: Found 2 interfaces for NID&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15232&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15210&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but was temporarily moved to a different project and moved back, so has a new &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15232&quot; title=&quot;sanity-lnet : @@@@@@ FAIL: Found 2 interfaces for NID&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15232&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15232&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ticket number.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
